ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 200, Nova Scotia
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 200 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the provision of financial assistance to the province of NOVA SCOTIA, with respect to the HEAVY RAINFALL from the remnants of Hurricane "Matthew" that occured from October 9 to 11, 2016.
